h’s book provides food for thought for readers in human geography, anthropology, sociology, urban studies, political science, international affairs, and post-Soviet and central Asian studies.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aCapitals (Cities)zAsia. 0aCity planningxPolitical aspectszAsia. 0aNew townsxPolitical aspectszAsia. 0aSpectacular, ThexPolitical aspectszAsia. 0aUrban renewalxPolitical aspectszAsia. 4aAsian Studies. 4aGeography-Physical & Cultural. 4aUrban Studies.  aauthoritarianism, Kazakhstan, Central Asia, urban geography, political geography.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311060655308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishz978311060425208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2018 Englishz978311060420708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2018z9783110603200oZDB-23-DPM40uhttps://doi.org/10.7591/978150172092540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501720925423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781501720925/original  a978-3-11-060420-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060425-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018 Englishb2018  a978-3-11-060655-3  Cornell University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DPMb2018